### <a id='2-9-alpha'></a> 2.9.0 Alpha 1

* **[Feature]** Operators can view and update internal authentication settings by using the <%= vars.ops_manager %> `/api/v0/settings/authentication` API endpoint or by accessing the **Settings** pane of the <%= vars.ops_manager %> UI.
* **[Feature]** Operators can update the <%= vars.ops_manager %> decryption passphrase by using the <%= vars.ops_manager %> `/api/v0/settings/decryption-passphrase` API endpoint.
* **[Feature]** Operators can view and update proxy settings in <%= vars.ops_manager %> by using the <%= vars.ops_manager %> `/api/v0/settings/proxy_settings` API endpoint.
* **[Feature]** When in Advanced Mode, operators can update additional fields related to blobstore location, Luna HSM, GCS blobstore and S3 blobstore settings in the **Director Config** screen after deploying the BOSH Director. Previously the fields were frozen after deployment.
* **[Feature]** <%= vars.ops_manager %> supports domain-style URLs as the default for configuring AWS S3 compatible blobstores.
* **[Feature]** <%= vars.ops_manager %> API documentation now follows the OpenAPI Specification (OAS). This update provides operators with a machine-parsable version of the <%= vars.ops_manager %> API docs and improves general formatting.
* **[UI Improvement]** When in Advanced Mode, operators see a special banner in the <%= vars.ops_manager %> UI.

